"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"The US president says Iran's leaders are gone and we could do a lot worse. Meanwhile, the UAE is responding to missile and drone threats from Iran. The US president might find that starting wars is easier than ending them, according to the BBC's international editor.\",            \"english_title\": \"US President on Iran\",            \"translated_version\": \"El presidente de EE.UU. dice que los l\u00edderes de Ir\u00e1n se han ido y podr\u00edamos estar peor. Mientras tanto, los Emiratos \u00c1rabes Unidos responden a amenazas de misiles y drones de Ir\u00e1n. El presidente de EE.UU. podr\u00eda encontrar que empezar guerras es m\u00e1s f\u00e1cil que terminarlas, seg\u00fan el editor internacional de la BBC.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Presidente de EE.UU. sobre Ir\u00e1n\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Norway's police attorney says they are investigating if a foreign state actor was involved. Witnesses report that drone strikes hit a residential building in Goma, often occupied by expatriates and aid workers.\",            \"english_title\": \"Norway Investigates Drone Strikes\",            \"translated_version\": \"El abogado de la polic\u00eda de Noruega dice que est\u00e1n investigando si un pa\u00eds extranjero estuvo involucrado. Testigos dicen que ataques de drones golpearon un edificio residencial en Goma, donde viven expatriados y trabajadores de ayuda.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Noruega Investiga Ataques de Drones\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The G7 group of nations supports the idea of releasing oil to address the rise in prices since the US-Israel war with Iran began. Iranians say they are staying at home and rarely going out as the US-Israeli bombing continues.\",            \"english_title\": \"G7 Supports Oil Release\",            \"translated_version\": \"El grupo G7 de naciones apoya la idea de liberar petr\u00f3leo para bajar los precios desde que comenz\u00f3 la guerra de EE.UU.-Israel con Ir\u00e1n. Los iran\u00edes dicen que se quedan en casa y salen poco mientras contin\u00faan los bombardeos de EE.UU.-Israel.\",            \"translated_title\": \"G7 Apoya Liberaci\u00f3n de Petr\u00f3leo\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Six Palestinians have been killed in attacks by settlers in the West Bank since Israel's war started, according to the UN. Russia claims the attack hit civilians and could not have happened without British help.\",            \"english_title\": \"Violence in West Bank\",            \"translated_version\": \"Seis palestinos han muerto en ataques de colonos en Cisjordania desde que comenz\u00f3 la guerra de Israel, seg\u00fan la ONU. Rusia dice que el ataque golpe\u00f3 a civiles y no podr\u00eda haber pasado sin ayuda brit\u00e1nica.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Violencia en Cisjordania\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Initial reports suggest a man with psychological problems set himself on fire on a bus, according to police. Bellarmine Mugabe will negotiate a plea deal after being accused of attempted murder and other charges in South Africa.\",            \"english_title\": \"Man Sets Bus on Fire\",            \"translated_version\": \"Informes iniciales dicen que un hombre con problemas psicol\u00f3gicos se prendi\u00f3 fuego en un autob\u00fas, seg\u00fan la polic\u00eda. Bellarmine Mugabe negociar\u00e1 un acuerdo despu\u00e9s de ser acusado de intento de asesinato y otros cargos en Sud\u00e1frica.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Hombre Prende Fuego a Autob\u00fas\"        }    ]}"